Makin my modem nigh unhackable What's the best way to setup a home network? Why should I care about BGP?
Post a reply
4 posts	• Page 1 of 1	Makin my modem nigh unhackable
by Tharos on Fri May 20, 2011 3:32 am	([msg=57596]see Makin my modem nigh unhackable[/msg])
Is basically what I''m going to try and do, As I tried hacking it with Aircrack, and it took me two minutes, which is kinda sad.So I'm going to try and make it near unhackable as much as I can. So Far I've got a new key, switching to WPA2 of course, And using a randomly generated 64-char key. I also am setting up the modem to filter MAC's, Only allowing ones I personally add to the list. Anything else I should know about to bulk up defenses anymore?Modem is an Actiontec M1000, If you know anything about it personally.Thanks
