Re: Makin my modem nigh unhackable
by afman on Sat Aug 06, 2011 4:36 pm	([msg=60631]see Re: Makin my modem nigh unhackable[/msg])
You probably already know this, but MAC address filtering is very easy to beat. An attacker can easily grab a computer's MAC address from sniffed traffic and spoof his own to be the same. The key however, will be fairly unbeatable.
